description:
A girl who came from France and wields two enormous double-edged swords (claymores) to fight.
She`s bound to the student council president Tokugawa Yoshihiko by a half-forced master and servant relationship.
As an assassin on Tokugawa`s side and unable to disobey him, she challenges Muneakira and his friends to fight.
name: Charles de d`Artagnan
